  "text": "From the above results, some interesting structure-activity relationships could be concluded: (1) the introduction of acyl-thiourea was significant for improving their activity; [CITATION_1] in HeLa, SK-OV-3 and MGC-803 assays, the antitumor activities were found to be in the order of ortho-> para-; (3) compared the antitumor activity of compounds 8 with 9, it could be found that the antitumor activity of compounds 9 were better than that of 8. It was important to note that the introduction of a benzene group at R1 was important for improving antitumor activities.",
