      "span_text": "From the above results, some interesting structure-activity relationships could be concluded: (1) the introduction of acyl-thiourea was significant for improving their activity; in HeLa, SK-OV-3 and MGC-803 assays, the antitumor activities were found to be in the order of ortho-> para-; (3) compared the antitumor activity of compounds 8 with 9, it could be found that the antitumor activity of compounds 9 were better than that of 8."
